cerpt_area": {"text": "我感觉任何工作（或公司）都有好坏，但是作为小白，来知乎贴吧这些论坛详细了解，容易相信网友说的，他们说不好我就也觉得不好了，然后就不想面试这家公司了。然后连续 4-5 个工作知乎网友都说不好（都是正规的校招，也有名企伊利什么的），而且几乎全是差评，我应该怎么办呢？感觉他们说的都有道理，但我自己也没出过社会工作，不知道他们的职场道理是对是错，害怕这样下去所有工作都不是好工作，最后找不到工作…有些网友说这个公司是自己的亲身经历千万别去，说的也挺真实的，但是有没有可能是竞争公司派来说坏话的？为什么没人说好话呢？我应该相信他们的意见吗？（想的比较多，不喜勿喷哈哈哈）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-04c086ddcbb6d56e4c6ce0c16e123eb0_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "157 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/498950804"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5N656umKs7NdEAMaCDczMTU5MDg3IJq4xowGMBg4yAZAFXIJNDk4OTUwODA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1637252073.332836", "card_id": "Q_498597978", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "乾隆白菜到底是凉菜还是啥东西？怎么做更正宗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8f28af038214d03a9632ca7c3f5913a1_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "152 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/498597978"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5N656umKs7NdEAMaCDczMDgwNzkxIP2ivYwGMAc4sgFAFnIJNDk4NTk3OTc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1637252073.333295", "card_id": "Q_499290554", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小说《水浒传》中，假如镇关西忍耐切了十斤软筋脆骨，鲁达会放过他吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-51fc2278187876c51e396888077fd9f6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "139 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/499290554"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I5N656umKs7NdEAMaCDczMjM0NzQ0ILiKzYwGMAI4HEAXcgk0OTkyOTA1NTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBA